1
00:00:36,320 --> 00:00:37,920
If you really brewed it,

2
00:00:38,159 --> 00:00:39,159
then however much we want,

3
00:00:39,159 --> 00:00:40,200
you should be able to provide, right?

4
00:00:40,679 --> 00:00:42,240
Then bring a hundred bottles tomorrow,

5
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:43,640
and we'll believe you.

6
00:00:43,640 --> 00:00:44,280
Exactly.

7
00:00:44,280 --> 00:00:45,640
That vinegar sold out long ago.

8
00:00:45,640 --> 00:00:46,880
It was booked up ages ago.

9
00:00:47,039 --> 00:00:47,920
If you guys want some,

10
00:00:47,920 --> 00:00:48,920
just wait for the next batch.

11
00:00:49,039 --> 00:00:50,479
Still lying.

12
00:00:50,840 --> 00:00:51,920
You kid,

13
00:00:52,520 --> 00:00:53,759
you're hopeless.

14
00:00:55,159 --> 00:00:55,960
Yingrong.

15
00:00:56,119 --> 00:00:58,520
The Baliang Vinegar in my shop is almost out.

16
00:00:58,520 --> 00:01:00,039
When is the next batch coming out?

17
00:01:00,119 --> 00:01:01,159
The time isn't set yet.

18
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:02,119
I'll hurry.

19
00:01:02,719 --> 00:01:03,560
Good, good, good.

20
00:01:07,079 --> 00:01:07,799
This vinegar,

21
00:01:07,799 --> 00:01:09,799
was really brewed by my second child.

22
00:01:09,920 --> 00:01:10,959
Of course.

23
00:01:11,239 --> 00:01:12,159
Is there any doubt?

24
00:01:12,719 --> 00:01:15,159
I got the stock directly from Yingrong.

25
00:01:15,719 --> 00:01:16,519
Yingrong.

26
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:17,719
I want to buy this vinegar.

27
00:01:17,719 --> 00:01:18,760
Save some for me.

28
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:19,480
Okay.

29
00:01:19,599 --> 00:01:20,280
Save a bit for me.

30
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:21,280
Yingrong.

31
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,079
Me too.

32
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:23,120
Sure thing.

33
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:24,280
Uncles and Aunties, there's enough for everyone.

34
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:25,159
Don't worry.

35
00:01:25,239 --> 00:01:26,359
What's there to be smug about?

36
00:01:26,359 --> 00:01:27,159
Smug.

37
00:01:27,439 --> 00:01:28,799
So what if she brewed it?

38
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:31,200
Is selling vinegar better than being a worker?

39
00:01:31,359 --> 00:01:32,920
It's not respectable work.

40
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:35,159
Whoever wants to do it can do it.

41
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:37,280
The Cement Factory's restructuring,

42
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:39,480
in these past few months,

43
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:42,599
has achieved very important success.

44
00:01:42,719 --> 00:01:43,799
In this,

45
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:46,959
we couldn't have done it without our comrade workers' efforts.

46
00:01:47,599 --> 00:01:48,760
During these few months,

47
00:01:49,239 --> 00:01:50,879
I saw a person,

48
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:52,480
who has solid technical skills,

49
00:01:52,799 --> 00:01:54,760
and excellent management ability.

50
00:01:55,079 --> 00:01:56,319
Such talent,

51
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:59,719
is exactly what the factory needs right now.

52
00:02:00,079 --> 00:02:00,799
Therefore,

53
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:03,560
after the factory's voting election,

54
00:02:03,959 --> 00:02:04,599
it is decided,

55
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,519
Comrade Zheng Minjiang,

56
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:09,159
will serve as the new Factory Director.

57
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,960
Good!

58
00:02:11,639 --> 00:02:13,080
Good!

59
00:02:13,479 --> 00:02:14,919
Good!

60
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:18,599
Now, let's invite Comrade Zheng Minjiang to speak.

61
00:02:18,879 --> 00:02:19,719
I object.

62
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:23,960
I object to an irresponsible person,

63
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:26,280
using nepotism to become Factory Director.

64
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:26,960
That's right.

65
00:02:27,159 --> 00:02:28,919
Why was he able to become Factory Director?

66
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:31,000
Just because he is Bureau Chief Zhen's student.

67
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,479
I firmly object.

68
00:02:32,479 --> 00:02:35,280
We support Director Zheng.

69
00:02:35,879 --> 00:02:44,120
We support Director Zheng.

70
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:46,000
Opportunist.

71
00:02:46,159 --> 00:02:47,280
You sellout.

72
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:50,159
Speaking of nepotism,

73
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:52,159
we really do need to investigate thoroughly.

74
00:02:53,039 --> 00:02:55,159
Some people lack technical skills,

75
00:02:55,439 --> 00:02:57,080
yet use family connections,

76
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:59,599
to occupy key leadership positions,

77
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:02,719
leading to inefficient factory management.

78
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:09,159
Nowadays in the eastern coastal regions,

79
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,879
there are many private enterprises.

80
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,479
Efficiency comes first.

81
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:16,759
For them, once the machines start,

82
00:03:17,039 --> 00:03:18,280
it brings in ten thousand taels of gold.

83
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:19,919
And us?

84
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,800
Some people think,

85
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:24,120
doing more or less is the same.

86
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:27,919
Leaving a few technical experts to work themselves to death.

87
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,560
After our factory restructures,

88
00:03:30,159 --> 00:03:32,319
the capable will stay,

89
00:03:32,759 --> 00:03:34,680
the incapable will leave.

90
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:39,960
Good!

91
00:03:44,879 --> 00:03:46,560
Now, I will announce

92
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:48,919
further appointments and position adjustments.

93
00:03:49,759 --> 00:03:51,960
Based on recommendations and voting, the factory

94
00:03:52,919 --> 00:03:53,639
has decided

95
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:54,919
to revoke

96
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:58,520
Comrade Li Guangming's position as Workshop Director.

97
00:03:58,879 --> 00:04:01,960
Director Wu, for selling factory positions,

98
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,719
is hereby

99
00:04:04,479 --> 00:04:05,599
suspended from duty.

100
00:04:05,639 --> 00:04:06,439
Additionally,

101
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,319
the factory wishes to commend

102
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,840
those who have recently

103
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:12,120
contributed their strength to the factory.

104
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:13,719
Especially

105
00:04:14,159 --> 00:04:16,079
Comrade Wang Yingzhu from the Accounting Department.

106
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:19,240
The factory has decided to promote her to

107
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,199
Finance Manager.

108
00:04:21,879 --> 00:04:28,279
Good!

109
00:04:30,879 --> 00:04:32,000
She gets promoted,

110
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:33,519
and I get removed?

111
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,279
On what grounds?

112
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,720
Director Zheng!

113
00:04:38,639 --> 00:04:39,480
Director Zheng!

114
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,279
Director Zheng!

115
00:04:42,879 --> 00:04:43,680
Sister Yingzhu.

116
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:45,040
You looking for me?

117
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,560
Inside the factory,

118
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,720
just call me Comrade Wang Yingzhu.

119
00:04:49,279 --> 00:04:50,759
It's like this, Director Zheng.

120
00:04:50,759 --> 00:04:54,000
I've only been in the Finance Department for a few months.

121
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:56,680
Suddenly becoming Finance Manager...

122
00:04:57,279 --> 00:04:58,800
isn't it a bit inappropriate?

123
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:01,920
Your position as Finance Manager wasn't arranged by me.

124
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:04,519
It was the factory leadership and the Finance Department

125
00:05:04,519 --> 00:05:06,160
who selected you through recommendations and voting.

126
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,079
So that's how it is.

127
00:05:08,759 --> 00:05:09,920
But Director Zheng,

128
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:12,759
our department has many veteran comrades.

129
00:05:13,319 --> 00:05:14,759
In terms of experience,

130
00:05:15,439 --> 00:05:17,360
I certainly can't compare to them.

131
00:05:17,759 --> 00:05:19,759
Although you just transferred to the Finance Department,

132
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,160
you work diligently.

133
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,639
And in the entire Accounting Department,

134
00:05:22,639 --> 00:05:24,079
you were the fastest to get your accounting certificate.

135
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,120
Alright then.

136
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:28,439
I'll give it a try.

137
00:05:30,279 --> 00:05:31,279
It's not just you.

138
00:05:31,839 --> 00:05:33,720
I'm actually a rookie too.

139
00:05:34,079 --> 00:05:36,920
So we need to achieve some results,

140
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:37,839
so we don't let down

141
00:05:37,839 --> 00:05:39,879
everyone's expectations and trust in us.

142
00:05:39,879 --> 00:05:40,720
Okay.

143
00:05:41,519 --> 00:05:42,319
Go get back to work.

144
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:50,439
Yingzhu

145
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:50,879
Yingzhu

146
00:05:50,959 --> 00:05:51,680
Listen to me.

147
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:52,360
Just listen to me for a second.

148
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,079
Just a few words.

149
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,120
Yingzhu

150
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,160
Yingzhu

151
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:58,319
You're so close with Zheng Minjiang.

152
00:05:58,319 --> 00:05:59,639
Put in a good word for me.

153
00:05:59,879 --> 00:06:01,759
I, Li Guangming, am a Workshop Director after all.

154
00:06:01,839 --> 00:06:04,519
How did I end up as a laid-off worker?

155
00:06:05,079 --> 00:06:07,199
The laid-off list has to go through the organization.

156
00:06:07,199 --> 00:06:08,879
It's not just up to the Factory Director.

157
00:06:09,199 --> 00:06:09,920
If you want to blame someone,

158
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:12,120
blame yourself for not focusing on the right path.

159
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:12,600
You...

160
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:14,160
You unwanted woman dare to lecture me?

161
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:14,560
I...

162
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:15,839
Li Guangming.

163
00:06:16,279 --> 00:06:17,879
We are already divorced.

164
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,879
If you dare touch me again,

165
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:21,519
I'm not someone to be messed with.

166
00:06:22,519 --> 00:06:23,240
Yingzhu.

167
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,519
Are you really not going to care about me?

168
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:25,680
What we had has to count for something.

169
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,120
Couples don't hold grudges overnight.

170
00:06:27,439 --> 00:06:28,480
Don't touch me.

171
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,279
We don't have any relationship anymore.

172
00:06:31,279 --> 00:06:32,519
We can remarry.

173
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,720
In your dreams.

174
00:06:34,639 --> 00:06:35,439
Yes.

175
00:06:36,079 --> 00:06:37,120
I used to be...

176
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,920
...a pushover you could manipulate.

177
00:06:39,519 --> 00:06:41,120
But I've made my decision now.

178
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:42,560
There's no turning back.

179
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,079
Yingzhu.

180
00:06:43,199 --> 00:06:43,600
Yingzhu.

181
00:06:43,839 --> 00:06:44,439
Yingzhu.

182
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,319
My wife is gone.

183
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:51,959
My job is gone.

184
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,079
What do I have left?

185
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,480
I, Li Guangming, still have a son.

186
00:06:56,759 --> 00:06:57,480
Right.

187
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,639
I still have a son.

188
00:06:59,319 --> 00:07:00,839
I can still go on with my life.

189
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:02,240
You all just wait.

190
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:03,720
Just wait.

191
00:07:04,199 --> 00:07:05,040
Sister Yingrong.

192
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:09,839
Did you come to rush the vinegar for your dad again?

193
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,480
I brought everyone some food.

194
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,639
Seeing how hard you work brewing vinegar,

195
00:07:13,639 --> 00:07:14,800
I came to see you.

196
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,040
Xiaochuan.

197
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:17,240
Come and eat.

198
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:17,800
Take a break.

199
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:18,680
Come have a bite.

200
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:24,639
Sister Yingrong.

201
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,560
Where is that Zheng Haiyang?

202
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,319
Where is he?

203
00:07:27,519 --> 00:07:28,600
He went out to haul goods.

204
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,600
He'll be back soon.

205
00:07:30,319 --> 00:07:31,199
I'll go meet him.

206
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,399
Zheng Haiyang.

207
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:42,800
Um...

208
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,000
My dad asked me to bring some food.

209
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:44,920
Come have some.

210
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:45,680
I'm not hungry yet.

211
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:46,879
You guys go eat first.

212
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,040
Zheng Haiyang.

213
00:07:52,519 --> 00:07:53,720
I allow you to pursue me.

214
00:07:56,839 --> 00:07:57,639
What did you say?

215
00:07:57,759 --> 00:07:58,639
I know.

216
00:07:58,639 --> 00:08:00,399
It must be because I have too many suitors,

217
00:08:00,399 --> 00:08:01,839
so you don't dare to confess, right?

218
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,079
Don't worry.

219
00:08:03,439 --> 00:08:05,120
I don't like any of them.

220
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:06,040
I don't like you.

221
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,800
You don't like me?

222
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:12,480
Then why did you help me before?

223
00:08:12,759 --> 00:08:14,279
You even cleared the stones from the road.

224
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:15,439
You even walked me home.

225
00:08:15,519 --> 00:08:17,240
I would have helped anyone else the same way.

226
00:08:17,639 --> 00:08:19,079
Besides, you are Boss Fang's daughter.

227
00:08:20,839 --> 00:08:21,639
Stop right there.

228
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:31,920
I don't care if you like me or not.

229
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,159
I'm just going to like you.

230
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:33,840
Zheng Haiyang.

231
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,759
I'm going to pursue you.

232
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,240
I won't give up.

233
00:08:52,039 --> 00:08:52,840
Xiao Tang

234
00:08:54,559 --> 00:08:55,360
Waiting for someone?

235
00:08:56,399 --> 00:08:57,399
Don't come over here

236
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,240
I'm waiting for my boyfriend

237
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,840
He might get the wrong idea

238
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,000
Yingtang

239
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:04,759
When you break up with your boyfriend

240
00:09:04,759 --> 00:09:05,960
Consider me

241
00:09:08,159 --> 00:09:09,000
What do you mean?

242
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:10,799
Hoping for my misfortune, are you?

243
00:09:10,799 --> 00:09:12,159
That's not what I meant

244
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,639
A toad lusting after a swan

245
00:09:15,799 --> 00:09:17,399
Compared to that boyfriend of yours, Tang Yan

246
00:09:17,399 --> 00:09:18,759
I'm much more sincere

247
00:09:18,759 --> 00:09:20,039
Love as solid as gold

248
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:22,840
Only poor people talk about "Love as solid as gold"

249
00:09:23,039 --> 00:09:24,240
If I follow you

250
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:25,679
I'll starve to death

251
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,919
I have a little money now

252
00:09:28,919 --> 00:09:30,200
Just give me a little more time

253
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,679
I will definitely buy a house

254
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:35,440
Then I'll be waiting until the sun rises in the west

255
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,240
Tang Yan

256
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:41,440
You're here

257
00:09:42,519 --> 00:09:43,200
Tang Yan

258
00:09:44,919 --> 00:09:45,440
What do you mean?

259
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:45,919
Yingtang

260
00:09:46,399 --> 00:09:47,200
Let's break up

261
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,240
Break up?

262
00:09:48,399 --> 00:09:49,200
Yes

263
00:09:49,559 --> 00:09:50,799
Why do you want to break up?

264
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:52,399
I won't break up

265
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:57,679
Yingtang, actually I really like you

266
00:09:57,759 --> 00:09:58,840
But don't you know

267
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:01,240
My dad would never agree to let me marry you

268
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:03,440
But you promised

269
00:10:03,799 --> 00:10:06,000
You said you'd take me and my parents to Hong Kong, China

270
00:10:06,159 --> 00:10:07,000
And

271
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:07,840
Sweet nothings like that

272
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,799
How could you believe them completely?

273
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:12,840
Use your brain

274
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:14,399
Hey

275
00:10:15,159 --> 00:10:16,080
You lied to me

276
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:16,799
Cut it out

277
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,159
You lied to me

278
00:10:18,159 --> 00:10:19,200
Stop making a scene

279
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:19,679
You lied to me

280
00:10:19,679 --> 00:10:20,080
Go then

281
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:20,720
Don't follow me

282
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:21,360
Tang Yan

283
00:10:21,639 --> 00:10:22,720
You big liar

284
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:23,240
Yingtang

285
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:23,960
Tang Yan

286
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:24,679
Don't cry

287
00:10:24,679 --> 00:10:25,360
I hate you

288
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:25,919
Hate you

289
00:10:25,919 --> 00:10:26,559
You still have me

290
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,200
I'd be better off dead

291
00:10:28,559 --> 00:10:29,120
Yingtang

292
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:30,000
Wait, wait

293
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,519
You've talked about jumping in the river since we were kids

294
00:10:32,519 --> 00:10:33,480
You're actually jumping?

295
00:10:33,799 --> 00:10:34,759
Don't save me

296
00:10:34,759 --> 00:10:35,799
Why do you care?

297
00:10:35,799 --> 00:10:36,519
No

298
00:10:36,799 --> 00:10:38,279
I've lost all face

299
00:10:38,279 --> 00:10:40,200
Face isn't as important as true love

300
00:10:40,679 --> 00:10:41,480
Get lost

301
00:10:41,559 --> 00:10:42,759
I don't want to see you

302
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:44,360
Wang Yingtang

303
00:10:44,799 --> 00:10:46,039
I like you

304
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:48,840
Whenever you figure it out

305
00:10:48,919 --> 00:10:50,159
Come find me anytime

306
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:03,279
Once Minjiang and Zhenzhen get married

307
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:05,200
And the second and third boys grow up

308
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:08,279
All my hard work as a mother these years

309
00:11:08,799 --> 00:11:10,440
Will finally be over

310
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:15,399
Haiyang

311
00:11:15,919 --> 00:11:16,720
Xiaochuan

312
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:19,720
What are you two doing here?

313
00:11:19,919 --> 00:11:21,120
Shouldn't you be at that

314
00:11:21,559 --> 00:11:22,480
...place Minjiang introduced you to

315
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:23,960
...working at the factory?

316
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,080
Mom, I...

317
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:27,320
Second Brother and I came out to stretch our legs

318
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,120
Right

319
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,919
I've been waiting forever

320
00:11:29,919 --> 00:11:32,519
Finally, you've brought me the vinegar

321
00:11:37,639 --> 00:11:38,519
You two

322
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:40,279
aren't working at Wang Yingrong's

323
00:11:40,279 --> 00:11:41,840
Vinegar Workshop, are you?

324
00:11:44,159 --> 00:11:46,639
Wang Shulan, you shameless thing!

325
00:11:46,639 --> 00:11:47,840
Get out here!

326
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:53,759
I was just looking for you!

327
00:11:53,759 --> 00:11:56,720
Your Wang family is full of heartless people!

328
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:58,240
You cheated my old man,

329
00:11:58,240 --> 00:11:59,879
and now you want to cheat my two sons!

330
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:02,080
Are you trying to destroy our Zheng family?

331
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:03,000
Auntie Chen, what are you doing?

332
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:03,840
Let go of me first.

333
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:05,000
Let me go first.

334
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:06,039
What do you want to do?

335
00:12:06,039 --> 00:12:07,039
Just let me go, okay?

336
00:12:07,039 --> 00:12:07,720
Mom!

337
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:09,399
We wanted to make vinegar ourselves.

338
00:12:09,399 --> 00:12:10,240
If we didn't want to do it,

339
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,120
no one could force us.

340
00:12:11,279 --> 00:12:12,399
That's right, Mom.

341
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:14,720
You two damn brats!

342
00:12:15,039 --> 00:12:16,399
Still defending her?

343
00:12:16,399 --> 00:12:17,200
Get out of my way!

344
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:19,879
Auntie Chen.

345
00:12:20,399 --> 00:12:22,399
I was the one who asked them to help back then.

346
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:24,000
I definitely didn't cheat anyone.

347
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,480
The factory is doing well now.

348
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:26,320
Baliang Vinegar is selling well.

349
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:27,200
You know that too.

350
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:29,639
The two of them definitely made money.

351
00:12:29,639 --> 00:12:31,480
Stop making a scene here now.

352
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:33,039
Don't make it sound so nice.

353
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:35,000
I don't agree, anyway.

354
00:12:35,279 --> 00:12:36,320
You two!

355
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:39,559
Running a Vinegar Workshop with those who killed your dad!

356
00:12:39,799 --> 00:12:41,919
If you don't quit,

357
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,360
I won't live past today!

358
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:45,039
I'll kill myself right in front of you!

359
00:12:45,639 --> 00:12:46,440
Mom!

360
00:12:48,759 --> 00:12:49,559
I...

361
00:12:49,879 --> 00:12:51,080
I'll kill you first!

362
00:12:51,159 --> 00:12:52,279
Then I'll kill myself!

363
00:12:56,639 --> 00:12:57,440
Mom!

364
00:12:57,639 --> 00:12:58,639
You're trying to stop me too?

365
00:12:58,639 --> 00:12:59,440
Is that it?

366
00:13:00,159 --> 00:13:01,399
You're all in on it!

367
00:13:01,399 --> 00:13:02,840
Ganging up to lie to me, aren't you?

368
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:04,840
I told you before

369
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:06,159
to get the two of them

370
00:13:06,159 --> 00:13:07,679
jobs at Mr. Tang's factory.

371
00:13:07,679 --> 00:13:10,080
But they ran off to work at the Vinegar Workshop!

372
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:10,799
You...

373
00:13:10,799 --> 00:13:12,320
You all ganged up to deceive me!

374
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,000
I... I...

375
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,639
I don't want to live anymore!

376
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:17,840
I can't go on living like this!

377
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:18,399
Mom.

378
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:19,279
Don't make a scene here.

379
00:13:19,279 --> 00:13:20,879
Let's go inside and talk.

380
00:13:20,919 --> 00:13:21,480
Yeah, Mom.

381
00:13:21,480 --> 00:13:22,200
You all lied to me!

382
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:22,559
Haiyang.

383
00:13:23,039 --> 00:13:23,480
Help Mom up.

384
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:24,440
You're useless!

385
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:25,240
Mom, let's go inside and talk.

386
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:26,840
After all I said,

387
00:13:26,919 --> 00:13:28,559
you still want to get mixed up with the Wang family!

388
00:13:28,559 --> 00:13:29,519
My second brother and I will explain.

389
00:13:29,519 --> 00:13:31,759
I should just die!

390
00:13:36,639 --> 00:13:37,639
Jianshe

391
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:40,720
Look at these sons of yours

392
00:13:43,919 --> 00:13:44,720
Mom

393
00:13:45,559 --> 00:13:46,360
This family

394
00:13:46,399 --> 00:13:47,879
shouldn't be carried by Big Brother alone

395
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:50,279
I want a career of my own

396
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:52,639
You going with Wang Yingrong to run a vinegar workshop

397
00:13:52,639 --> 00:13:54,600
is just nonsense

398
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:56,240
I know how to brew vinegar now

399
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:57,559
I finally feel

400
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:59,000
like I'm a useful person

401
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:01,120
Why can't I choose the path I like?

402
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:02,440
Exactly, Mom

403
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:03,840
You don't know how our Baliang Vinegar

404
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:04,600
sells so well

405
00:14:04,759 --> 00:14:07,720
How can selling vinegar compare to being a worker?

406
00:14:08,039 --> 00:14:09,960
You clearly have better prospects

407
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:11,879
Why do you want to do that

408
00:14:11,879 --> 00:14:13,519
shameful work?

409
00:14:13,879 --> 00:14:14,960
I don't think it's shameful

410
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:16,879
Sister Yingrong is amazing

411
00:14:16,879 --> 00:14:18,279
I want to strive alongside her

412
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:19,799
Selling vinegar with Sister Yingrong

413
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:21,559
we can make big money

414
00:14:21,559 --> 00:14:22,679
She even let us invest

415
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:23,960
You're even investing?

416
00:14:24,519 --> 00:14:26,639
Once you invest, you'll be even more inseparable

417
00:14:27,399 --> 00:14:28,039
Eldest

418
00:14:28,039 --> 00:14:29,639
say something

419
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:30,759
Mom

420
00:14:31,639 --> 00:14:32,720
I agree with them running the vinegar workshop

421
00:14:34,360 --> 00:14:35,600
All of you

422
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:38,200
have been bewitched by that Wang Yingrong

423
00:14:38,600 --> 00:14:39,159
Mom

424
00:14:39,519 --> 00:14:41,559
I just want to make vinegar with Yingrong
